  ('medical-tech-moex-20838', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關Lewis血型之敘述，何者正確？ 新生兒紅血球Lewis血型抗原之表現，與母親相同；因Lewis抗原物質可經胎盤傳到胎兒血液，為紅血球吸收 Lewis抗原之結構為穿膜7次的蛋白質（7-transmembrane protein），近似G蛋白，但無訊息傳導作用 Anti-Lea為冷型抗體，不具臨床意義 白種人因族群特有Sew基因，所以有25%表現Le ( a+b+ )', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:16+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5302e461d166", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a16ccf6383bd", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20839', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '成分分離術（apheresis），在進行血漿交換治療，執行一個血液體積之置換時，原有血漿成分移除率大致是 多少？ 100%  90%  70%  50%', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:16+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5302e461d166", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a16ccf6383bd", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
